name: Sri

reviews.review_text: I had an amazing experience at this hotel! The host, Richard, is a professional chef from England, and he serves some of the best-quality food in Goa. Every dish was crafted with perfection, offering a delightful blend of flavors and freshness. The hospitality was top-notch, and the attention to detail was evident in every aspect of the service. If you’re looking for a place with exceptional food and a warm, welcoming atmosphere, this is the spot! Highly recommended!

I came across this place via maps and it’s definitely going in my visit-again list. Amazing food, so nice and laid back vibe with a perfect location. The Goan style fish appetiser was a delight. Potato chips, just like we wanted with a homemade spicy green chutney. The server (didn’t get his name) was friendly and very attentive. The best thing is the cats and dogs around the place, if you want only then they will come to you. It was lovely to have a wholesome meal in this place.

Sri is the quentissential laid back warm spirit of goa. No rush here. Just enjoy the time and the great food that's about to be served. Richard probably the first pioneers of returning to the call of the motherland, has always kept the vibe and the food great. Visit this place for a taste of what all of goa should be.

description:
Nestled in the charming village of Siolim, **Sri** captures the essence of Goan culture with its inviting ambiance and delectable seafood offerings. Boasting an impressive **4.3-star rating** from **814 reviews**, this gem has become a beloved destination for both locals and tourists seeking a warm, laid-back dining experience.

### Ambiance & Design
From the moment you arrive at Sri, you're enveloped in a serene atmosphere that is quintessentially Goan. The garden setting is adorned with lush greenery, making it feel like an oasis where time slows down. The décor is rustic yet inviting, with charming details that evoke a sense of comfort and warmth. The combination of natural light filtering through leaves and soft background music creates an idyllic retreat perfect for family meals or intimate dinners. The presence of friendly cats and dogs roaming the premises adds an extra layer of charm, ensuring that your meal comes with a side of coziness and companionship.

![Relaxed outdoor seating in the garden](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnsEiS9z2J_x9CX-NsNZ9LBFO0xH8WjLRv8ClcglYvL1pigqs1ADG-YQcQX5yILWO7KYT7K7SZ_NcmuSUGvDCOhVA0QKYXC0fGA59xVVO0EForKwJH0DjIU9OuTlqGp-dbW_Rnx=w375-h281-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience
Sri's menu is a delightful homage to the region's culinary traditions, with a strong emphasis on **seafood** that has earned rave reviews. Signature dishes like the Goan-style fish appetizer showcase the owner Richard’s expertise; having honed his craft in England, he brings a unique twist to local flavors and ingredients. Dishes are elegantly presented, with fresh ingredients that burst with flavor, making every bite a surprise. Vegetarian options are also available for those looking to explore the refreshing local produce.

![Exquisite seafood dish](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdlNklHq6rbiy_l-r3CelrGC8oOe-JU_bcn1zd1rhe6T6qlHnVG_gklHwSc0qkPIfgS89CKKHBYDmdvzTiRXY9tfx2BQxmTsd_d55wJHQ2Br6CZDlu0xmMgNwduXn9sBlbyr9-jMOg=w375-h563-p)

### Customer Experience & Service
The service at Sri is frequently highlighted in customer reviews, with staff noted for their friendliness and attentiveness. Many describe their experiences as personalized and welcoming, perfectly complementing the restaurant's atmosphere. Richard, the host, is often commended for not only his culinary skills but for cultivating a friendly environment where guests feel at home. Whether you make a reservation or drop in spontaneously, be prepared for a laid-back experience where every aspect of service comes with a touch of care.

### Popularity & Reviews
The buzz surrounding Sri is palpable, with many patrons vowing to return after their first visit. It has garnered a reputation as a top-notch dining spot in the area, often mentioned favorably on various social media platforms. Guests consistently praise the balanced combination of quality food, pleasant service, and an atmosphere reminiscent of the easy-going life in Goa. Richard has successfully captured the spirit of the region, which keeps diners coming back for more.

![Charming garden atmosphere](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnSmcYlkWpi3gBI-jRJ2SXKesUghWLkVfkLzFPUGxIygBm5lkzTX0DHCgFJx5nEorj-XcK8aPyu9I-lIU9Wms4QWkwO4VAz_GL1pE6iW0m2VAD2RCt88UjBXg0sY9vKn6pC8KZQ=w375-h281-p)

### Conclusion
In summary, Sri in Siolim is more than just a restaurant; it is a celebration of Goan culture, culinary artistry, and heartfelt hospitality. With a lush garden setting, an enticing seafood menu, and a commitment to exceptional service, it's a destination that promises not just a meal, but an experience filled with flavor and joy. Highly recommended for anyone looking to indulge in the true essence of Goa, this restaurant has etched its place in the hearts of all who dine there.
